headline: UnitedHealthcare, Humana are gaming Medicare Advantage risk adjustment, analysis finds
summary: The research from the Alliance for Community Health Plans adds to existing evidence that major insurers are unfairly profiting from MA’s risk adjustment system, driving billions of dollars in unnecessary costs.
